pullRequest.body:
Given a morphism property P and a functor F, we define the morphism property `P.relative` of morphisms in the codomain of `F`. This is defined as being relatively representable with respect to `F`, and that any represented pullback of the morphism satisfies P.

Co-authored-by: JoÃ«l Riou <rioujoel@gmail.com>
